        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 via-teal-300 to-green-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Caesar Cipher<br>Encryption Tool</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Learn Cryptography by Encrypting and Decrypting Messages in Real-time</p>
        <button id="tryNowBtn" class="mt-8 px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-cyan-600/30 border border-cyan-400 font-semibold text-cyan-100 hover:bg-cyan-500/40 transition-all text-lg shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/20">✨ Try Now ✨</button>
